{"tid":2136680,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[香港正式成為大陸城市］香港有三千個醫療化驗師驗到武肺，仆街話唔夠人手送支那7隻專家嚟拎FNA","createTime":"2020-08-02T10:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T09:01:36.000Z","uid":137078,"like":99,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"169095808f4d8ff0347ca84d4236db5e4d0d2ebb","tid":2136680,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:29:30.000Z","msg":"1   2017 年有關醫務化驗師的醫療衞生服務人力統計調查(醫務化驗師統計調查)，涵蓋截至調查點算當日(即2017 年3 月 31 日)已根據《輔助醫療業條例》（第 359 章）的規定，於香港醫務化驗師管理委員會註冊的醫務化驗師。<br />\n1.2   所涵蓋醫務化驗師的人數為3 426 名。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有關驗口水，因為係biohazards infectious sample, 基本上除咗研究，日常驗係由醫療化驗師做，有牌先驗到<br />\n驗武肺還武肺，唔會拎嚟驗埋gonome，都係專業操守要跟，同埋係冇需要咁做<br />\n<br />\n佢哋運作上凌駕晒香港現行行果套，美其名為抗疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但由港共想推濕鳩健康瑪開始，專搵支那背景化驗所，過咗幾十億水比佢哋冇人提<br />\n可以起我底睇下乜公司<br />\n<br />\n依家佢直情唔同你扮，一次過落晒嚟<br />\n抗疫喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人，準備好住集中營未？"},{"pid":"bcbcfc2f741008e27fa288aa95e869aa6624bc47","tid":2136680,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:32:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8179f788a565dfad4145a7071d237655371dc35f","tid":2136680,"uid":82640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:33:44.000Z","msg":"同大陸人去台灣地震救災一樣<br />\n打下卡而已<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f2145f80682cae4324b164e13eb9a74efd382d","tid":2136680,"uid":137078,"like":42,"dislike":4,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yc6CZ1t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"http